Value: S2 Resources Ltd explores for and evaluates mineral properties in Australia and Finland. The company primarily explores for gold, nickel, copper, and platinum-group elements deposits. It holds interests in the Aarnivalkea prospect and Rupoas project located in Finland; and the Jillewarra, West Murchison, Three Springs, Koonenberry, Fraser Range, and Polar Bear projects located in Australia. The company was incorporated in 2015 and is based in Osborne Park, Australia.
